						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">tokumaru wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent"><div class="quotetitle">Sik wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">At least it has the sprite scaling bug fixed (which is why Virtua Fighter Mini takes advantage of it).</div><br />What sprite scaling bug?</div><br />Only the first four of the eight sprites on a scanline can be stretched horizontally. This bug is fixed in the SMS 2 and Game Gear. (<a href="http://www.smspower.org/uploads/Development/msvdp-20021112.txt" class="postlink">Source</a>, beginning at &quot;sprite pixels are zoomed to double&quot;)</div>

